[_Reluctant Dragon_](http://reluctant-dragon.blogspot.com/2008/02/patriotic-
youth-of-serbia-wears-prada.html) and [_Gray
Falcon_](http://grayfalcon.blogspot.com/2008/02/empires-ostpolitik.html) offer
two different perspectives on what it feels like being a Serb in the United
States following Kosovo's declaration of independence.

